ass=\"toc-text\">2. Codex CLI — 命令类似，格式略有不同</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%9A%E7%94%A8-codex-mcp-add-%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4\"><span class=\"toc-text\">方法一：用 codex mcp add 命令</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E4%BA%8C%EF%BC%9A%E6%89%8B%E5%8A%A8%E7%BC%96%E8%BE%91-TOML-%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6\"><span class=\"toc-text\">方法二：手动编辑 TOML 配置文件</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#3-OpenCode-%E2%80%94-%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87-JSON-%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6\"><span class=\"toc-text\">3. OpenCode — 通过 JSON 配置文件</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#4-%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%EF%BC%88%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%EF%BC%89\"><span class=\"toc-text\">4. 安全配置（重要）</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#5-%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E7%94%A8%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E8%AF%AD%E8%A8%80%E6%9F%A5%E8%AF%A2%EF%BC%9F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">5. 怎么用自然语言查询？</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%9F%A5%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE\"><span class=\"toc-text\">查数据</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%9C%8B%E8%A1%A8%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84\"><span class=\"toc-text\">看表结构</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE\"><span class=\"toc-text\">分析数据</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#6-%E6%8E%92%E9%94%99%E5%B0%8F%E8%B4%B4%E5%A3%AB\"><span class=\"toc-text\">6. 排错小贴士</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Dxc","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/images/avatar.png","link":"/","description":"Free will is not free. <br /> @ <b>公众号：精准拔草</b> <span style=\"display:inline;white-space:nowrap\"><sv